title: STAT+: Inside HHS’ anti-fraud efforts: An aggressive crackdown sweeps up mainly Democratic-led states
description: As it seeks to crack down on health care fraud, the Trump administration has put entire states in its crosshairs, notably those with Democratic leadership.
